    </lead_sponsor>
  </sponsors>
  <source>Hadassah Medical Organization</source>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Our aim is examine avenues by which mothers can transmit their trauma to their children.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      The goal of the study is to test for genetic bases and Gene x Environment interactions on the
      development of difficulties, particularly stress disorders, in young children whose mother
      were exposed to terror before they were born.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
